					h1: a(href='http://wex.vc/prefixo9/', target='_blank') Prefixo 9
					p Prefixo 9 reads your entire Gmail contact book and suggests changes for the ninth digit for cellphones for your contacts, that came into effect in several parts of Brazil starting 2012.
					p I've developed the site strongly using PHP, since updating Gmail contacts is exclusively done in XML. Afterwards I've updated the site renewing its visual, using Bootstrap.
