						time.dtend(datetime='2013-05') May 2013
				article.home-project.home-project-uvideos
					h1: a(href='http://videos.univision.com/', target='_blank') UVideos
					p UVideos was a huge refactoring of Univision's video portal, including complete TV shows, as well as clips, news, soap operas, music videos, etc.
					p I've developed a series of interactive components, such as the watchlist and recently watched videos, and related and recommended videos. As part of the project, I've proposed a clean and modularized JavaScript code, with full refactoring, that ultimately got into the entire portal, becoming the company's standard. Besides that, I've integrated internal applications, as well as third party APIs.
			section.home-company.home-company-mtv
				header
					h1: a(href='http://www.mtv.com.br/', rel='nofollow', target='_blank', title='MTV Brasil') MTV Brasil
